Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for that sun to shine endlessly, without wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for those clouds to drift through the blue skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for the freedom to sleep in as late as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bunch of people to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yukki, are you doing volunteer work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm motivated by more than just money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, if you don't hurry it up, they'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Chizuru want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes things easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do? Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told you that I'm not interested in going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one minute. Just talk to me for one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a minute to talk, don't you, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll make your skin silky-smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, a door-to-door salesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chizuru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you found your way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free? Do you want to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join me? {timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was making snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never done it before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but since we're on vacation, \NI thought I'd give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. Can you mix that dough for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-kun, you're good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again. I'm still learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does. I hope it turns out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-chan, that's no fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's deliciously sweet and light in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing how they'll turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we're finished, \Nwe should take them to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this strange feeling?\N It's like I'm not really myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've come this far, \Nwe should finish making...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Making what? A new me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted someone to hang out with,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so you went to everyone's houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone's hiding in the cool air of their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a whole month ahead of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm sure there will be opportunities to play outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be cool at night, and I'm pretty sure everyone would go if I invite them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-chan, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I think I'll have a wonderful summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone should have their own Shun-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, I can start to enjoy my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they didn't have anything smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Need help carrying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should learn to accept others' kindness...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is! The invitation to the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. "Can everyone make it? Let me know."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shun-chan invited me to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was how our summer began.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A Japanese festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a festival, you should to wear a yukata! It's refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you buy a baby chick at a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't buy one. Our apartment doesn't allow pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many to choose from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many that I don't know where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? I can't decide, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not just "something"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As students, we don't have a large budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't carefully and precisely choose the right food stall, we'll regret it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are so many choices... \NI don't know what to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In a situation like this, start with the classics! First off, we'll go with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all buy something different and share?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Yuutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A high schooler who knows his festivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the plan that praise-worthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a really good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it around already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll have your fair chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight breaks out every time we buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna hold on to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll eat it so you don't get fat, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Her hair's kinda fluffy, like a sheep's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted one when I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could never get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goldfish are so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Shun-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Masaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You going for it, Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you don't know what you're doing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It rips! That thing rips!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your consolation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so down about it. You almost got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And why do you keep calling me "Mary"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me weird nicknames!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop it. Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt. I came to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Masaki-chan okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get close--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a consolation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets super mad at me, \Nbut treats Shun-chan like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry, but I'm not any good at cheering people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't laugh with anyone except Shun anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear the melody of love bubbling beneath the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not underneath the surface. It's obviously above!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? So that's why she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NAre you boys rookies, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This paper's too thin \Nto catch anything that's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's the point of a game like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it shows no respect for their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Value is subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His business is making a game of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a generous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he gave us five layers of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught so many goldfish that I had to return some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you did something to make him do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But why Shun-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the least manly of all of us, and like, more cute than cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, if we're just talking about his face, he's my type...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! That's not what this is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, you don't even know why you like or dislike someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she look like a sheep in a flock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shun-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we should help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hisako, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan. {taimingu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaname-kun. So you're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kaname-kun's friend, Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to set off some fireworks later?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise it'll be a wonderful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you make {\i1}that{\i0} plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If love always went according to plan, heartbreak wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They should sell fireworks at the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's one nearby, so I'll go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We were just saying it'd be nice to get out of the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Shun-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them are going shopping for fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay. Don't get flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have the keyring that Shun-chan gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Masaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay. Don't get flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just start from over there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go off by yourself, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting so tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll help you look—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, an attitude isn't going to make your flat chest—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yukki! Forget her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to search by yourself, try not to look so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after I said not to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want us to help look?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so beat up, Chizuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It cost 700 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty crowded from here to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei! The class is trying to work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but Yuuta-kun isn't participating seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta-kun, I know you want to look at the girls outside in gym class,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have to put some effort in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Found what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, shorty. Is that really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped that bear. Could I have it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That? I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's the one who dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any proof, you can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, shoot it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,300 yen per round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never grow up to become that kind of adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, you'll never become that kind of person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he'd make something he found a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you let your emotions get to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get emotional, \Nyou won't be able to aim properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too calm about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you shouldn't laugh at people who are trying their hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Kaname's best effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Yuutan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be hard with such a small target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's not easy! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We should rely on someone who's cleared countless missions before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The size of the target doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill or be killed. That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not {\i1}that{\i0} serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you aiming at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't choose between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They got the fireworks, so they're coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shun-chan's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll know I dropped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, I need some bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already paying with bills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for saving money by sharing food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get it, you're paying me back, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You have one shot left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who said I could do it if I fired enough shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm just wasting money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Namu... Namu... Namu... Namu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is a young girl like you chanting, "Namu, namu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe that's why I managed to hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We bought fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one who got it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Amazing. There are so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We have more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fire them off together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we save the sparklers for last?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get too close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one coming towards {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-kun, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the fireworks gently nudged back the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everyone's smiles were there as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A firework's glow is short lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,just like your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't stop playing around, you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they'd mess around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wielding fireworks is a serious contest.
